<Defs>

	<!-- Ork - Slugga -->
	<ThingDef ParentName="O21BaseMakeableGun">
		<defName>OrkSlugga</defName>
		<label>Slugga</label>
		<description>A slugga iz da ork equivalent uv a space marine bolt pistol. It iz usually paired wit' a choppa, an mobs uv boyz 'oo karry 'da two are kalled slugga boyz. Due ta ‘da ramshackle nature uv ork weaponry, every slugga iz different, but most if not all sluggas are semi-automatic, large kalibre side arms. Dough not as sophisticated as most otha weapons used ‘n ‘da imperium, sluggas are no less effective dan other, more advanced side arms when used korrectly. As far as ‘da melee-focused ork hold'n it iz koncerned, ‘da effectiveness uv a slugga iz uv little importance, as long as it iz big an' makes a loud noise when it fires.</description>
		<graphicData>
			<texPath>Things/Ork/Weapons/Ranged/Slugga</texPath>
			<graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>		
    </graphicData>
		<soundInteract>Interact_Autopistol</soundInteract>
		<statBases>
			<WorkToMake>32000</WorkToMake>
			<MarketValue>750</MarketValue>
			<Mass>2</Mass>
			<AccuracyTouch>0.50</AccuracyTouch>
			<AccuracyShort>0.55</AccuracyShort>
			<AccuracyMedium>0.40</AccuracyMedium>
			<AccuracyLong>0.30</AccuracyLong>
			<RangedWeapon_Cooldown>0.85</RangedWeapon_Cooldown>
		</statBases>
	<recipeMaker>
		<researchPrerequisite>O21_Ork_Weapons_Basic</researchPrerequisite>
	</recipeMaker>
		<equippedStatOffsets>
			<ShootingAccuracyPawn>-0.1</ShootingAccuracyPawn>
			<PsychicSensitivity>-0.5</PsychicSensitivity>
			<MoveSpeed>0.5</MoveSpeed>
		</equippedStatOffsets>
		<verbs>
			<li>
				<verbClass>Verb_Shoot</verbClass>
				<hasStandardCommand>true</hasStandardCommand>
				<defaultProjectile>O21_Bullet_Slugga</defaultProjectile>
				<warmupTime>0.3</warmupTime>
				<range>26</range>
				<soundCast>Shot_Revolver</soundCast>
				<soundCastTail>GunTail_Light</soundCastTail>
				<muzzleFlashScale>8</muzzleFlashScale>
			<targetParams>
				<canTargetLocations>true</canTargetLocations>
			</targetParams>
			</li>
		</verbs>
    <tools>
      <li>
        <label>grip</label>
        <capacities>
          <li>Blunt</li>
        </capacities>
        <power>12</power>
        <cooldownTime>1.6</cooldownTime>
      </li>
      <li>
        <label>barrel</label>
        <capacities>
          <li>Blunt</li>
          <li>Poke</li>
        </capacities>
        <power>12</power>
        <cooldownTime>1.6</cooldownTime>
      </li>
    </tools>
		<techLevel>Spacer</techLevel>
		<weaponTags>
			<li>OrkRanged</li>
			<li>Slugga</li>
		</weaponTags>
		<thingCategories>
			<li>OrkRanged</li>
		</thingCategories>
		<tradeTags>
			<li>OrkRanged</li>
		</tradeTags>
		<costList>
			<ComponentIndustrial>1</ComponentIndustrial>
			<Plasteel>2</Plasteel>
			<Steel>10</Steel>
		</costList>
	</ThingDef>
	
