	<!-- Ork - Shoota -->
	<ThingDef ParentName="O21BaseMakeableGun">
		<defName>OrkShoota</defName>
		<label>Shoota</label>
		<description>A shoota iz a kinetic, ballistic weapon used by da orks ‘dat iz chosen not for its efficiency but for da amount uv noise it makes an’ da amount uv damage it kan do. ‘da best shootas are deafen'n an' deadly 'n equal measure. Like da slugga, shootas are not very accurate. Dis suits da orks jus fine since dey seem less interested ‘n accuracy dan ‘n kaus'n damage an' rais'n a ruckus. 'da noise uv a shoota will give orks a morale boost an' kan kause enemiez ta lose dere morale an' retreat from 'da overpower'n noise uv dozens uv shootas. None ‘da less, mobs uv shoota boyz make up for dere lack uv accuracy wit' ‘da shea volume uv fire directed at dere targets.</description>
		<graphicData>
			<texPath>Things/Ork/Weapons/Ranged/Shoota</texPath>
			<graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>		
